#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.audiotube.appdata.xml:125
msgid ""
"AudioTube can search YouTube Music, list albums and artists, play "
"automatically generated playlists, albums and allows to put your own "
"playlist together. It is adapted to mobile phones and desktop computers."
msgstr ""
"AudioTube lahko išče YouTube Music, navaja albume in izvajalce, predvaja "
"samodejno ustvarjene sezname predvajanja, albume in omogoča sestavljanje "
"lastnega seznama predvajanja. Prilagojena je mobilnim telefonom in namiznim "
"računalnikom."

